race.description: Tamworth City Toyota Country Music Cup Showcase Hcp
race.comment: CHANDON STAR (8) tough gelding chasing the hat-trick and saves his best for this course. Big jump in class when taken to the front for a soft on-pace victory over 1100m at Gilgandra in fast time. Proven at the trip and he gets the right run again. Leading player. KRANICH (3) progressive gelding resuming who looks well weighted with Stiff's 3kg claim. Finished a narrow second over the mile at Randwick in Highway class last prep and since fitted with the 1000m trial placing. Hard to hold out. NIGHT FIGHTER (5) has gone to a new level this campaign and has excellent credentials on his home track and at this trip. Winning rider goes back aboard from the good draw. Expected to bounce back. ZAMBORGHINI (6) five-weeks between runs for the new yard when a disappointing thirteenth at Inverell over 1400m. Proven at the trip with the key jockey change. Each-way.
